0in%20high%20school.%20Oh%20well.%20At%20least%20I'm%20learning%20it%20now%2C%20I%20guess.%20Also%20if%20you%20need%20someone%20to%20make%20basic%20and%20obnoxiously%2090's%20website%2C%20I'm%20your%20idiot.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20I%20can't%20get%20enough%20of%20is%20gifs%2C%20if%20you%20can't%20tell.%20Hey%2C%20if%20the%20Internet%20users%20of%20the%2090's%20and%202000's%20can%20use%20a%20metric%20assload%20of%20gifs%20on%20their%20personal%20websites%2C%20why%20can't%20I%3F%20It%20adds%20to%20the%20shittiness.%20It's%20like%20the%20garnish%20on%20top%20of%20a%20fancy%20dish.%20Except%20it's%20a%20plate%20of%20garnished%20shit%20instead.%20I%20don't%20know%20where%20I%20was%20going%20with%20this%20analogy.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Chr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJuly%2023%2C%202020%3C%2Fb%3E%20-%20Edited%20the%20CSS%20to%20get%20two%20separate%20elements%20side%20by%20side%20on%20this%20particular%20page.%20It%20looks%20like%20hot%20garbage.%20I%20love%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Chr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3E%20%3Cb%3EAugust%2016%2C%202020%3C%2Fb%3E%20-%20After%203%20weeks%20of%20being%20away%2C%20I%20added%20a%20new%20hidden%20page%3F%20Why%3F%20It's%20a%20joke%20referencing%20a%20game%20of%20%3Ci%3EFiasco!%3C%2Fi%3E%20I%20was%20recently%20in%2C%20don't%20question%20iut.%20Also%20if%20you%20can%20figure%20out%20which%20exactly%20playset%20it's%20referencing%2C%20you%20win%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Chr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%3Cp%3E%20%3Cb%3EJuly%2028%2C%202021%3C%2Fb%3E%20-%20Guess%20who%20got%20back%20into%20developing%20this%20website%3F%20Me%2C%20bitches.%20Totally%20not%20plugging%20my%20forum%20and%20my%20Newgrounds%2C%20no%20siree...%20aight%2C%20ya%20got%20me.%20But%20there's%20more%20to%20editing%20my%20site%20than%20that.%20I%20don't%20have%20HUGE%20future%20plans%2C%20but%20I'd%20still%20like%20to%20expand%20and%20spiff%20up%20this%20for%20extra%20webcore-ness.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%20%20%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%20